3.content: Getting started . Dependencies . Astrocook requires the following packages: . Astropy 3.2.2 | SciPy 1.3.1 | Specutils 0.6 | NumPy 1.17.3 | LmFit 0.9.14 | Cycler 0.10.0 | StatsModels 0.10.1 | matplotlib 3.1.1 | Sphinx 2.2.0 | . Installation . GitHub . Clone the GitHub repository on your local machine: git clone https://github.com/DAS-OATs/astrocook . | Fetch the last commit of the develop branch git fetch origin develop . | Docker .
